---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="About" description="How Prompt Pantry works — AI-researched recipes for real kitchens.">
  <article class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 py-10">
    <h1 class="font-display text-4xl md:text-5xl text-charcoal mb-6">About Prompt Pantry</h1>

    <div class="recipe-prose text-warm-gray">
      <p class="text-lg text-charcoal">
        Prompt Pantry is a recipe site where every dish is researched and written by AI — and we're upfront about that.
      </p>

      <h2>How recipes are made</h2>
      <p>
        Each recipe goes through a rigorous research pipeline. First, a dedicated research session
        scours the internet for renowned versions of a dish — professional techniques, chef insights,
        regional variations, and the culinary science behind what makes each dish work. That research
        is then synthesized into an original recipe that combines the best approaches into something
        cohesive and practical.
      </p>
      <p>
        These aren't throwaway AI-generated recipes. They're research-backed syntheses built from
        the collective knowledge of professional kitchens, food science, and culinary tradition.
      </p>

      <h2>Why this exists</h2>
      <p>
        Because good recipes shouldn't require scrolling past a 2,000-word essay about someone's
        trip to Tuscany. Prompt Pantry gives you well-researched, clearly written recipes with
        useful tools — serving scalers, ingredient checklists, step timers, and cook mode for
        hands-free use in the kitchen.
      </p>

      <h2>How to use this site</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <strong>Serving scaler</strong> — Adjust the number of servings and all ingredient
          quantities update automatically.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Ingredient checkboxes</strong> — Check off ingredients as you prep them
          for easy mise en place tracking.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Cook mode</strong> — A distraction-free, step-by-step view that keeps
          your screen awake while you cook.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Step timers</strong> — Tap any timer in a recipe step to start a countdown
          right in the page.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Technique guides</strong> — Linked explanations of fundamental cooking
          techniques referenced throughout recipes.
        </li>
      </ul>

      <h2>A note on trust</h2>
      <p>
        AI-generated content has a well-earned reputation for being unreliable. We take this
        seriously. The research pipeline is designed to ground every recipe in real culinary
        knowledge rather than hallucinated ingredient lists. That said, always use your judgment
        in the kitchen — taste as you go, adjust seasoning, and trust your senses.
      </p>
    </div>
  </article>
</Layout>
